name: Unidentified_Theelin_Jedi
content: A Theelin Jedi served in the Jedi Order during the time of the High Republic Era. The Theelin and an Aki-Aki Jedi traveled to the Outer Rim astronomical object Blarrum, searching for the beast-trader Triv Blago, who dealt in the illegal capture and transportation of dangerous animals. The two Jedi tracked down Blago in Kul Kenada Spaceport, where the trader was dealing with the monster hunter Ty Yorrick. The Jedi confronted Blago, with the Theeling ordering him to surrender. Yorrick fled on a speeder, abandoning Blago to the Jedi, who took the trader into custody.
